Title:
    Let's Install Node.js and Do Cool Stuff With It! #100Devs 

Mayanwolfe Streams Link:
    https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VOfqO4-RLd4

Notes:
******

Launch a server:
    $ node <filename>
    $ node server // No need to add file extension

Close server:
    $ Crl + c

Install a node module
    $ npm i <package_name>
    $ npm i figlet
    // Will create:
        // package.json
        // package-lock.json
        // node_modules folder

